item.title: [317] Where can I download runescape models and put them on my server?
item.dc:creator: @the1337legend the1337legend
item.description:
@the1337legend wrote:

watch n lern:

it depends on which models you want there are tons… but if you want pvp armor models i suggest using demisepking’s get from download section

no.

@topic.

You need a rs model grabber, something like RSMV works fine, use that along with DatMaker and if it’s not a cape/plate/legs you can animate it to move in game, then simply add to the respective place, if you don’t already have a models folder for specific models, say a 554 server, which most likely doesn’t have that, you will need to learn how to do it correctly, perhaps a tutorial.
